org.forgerock.openam.core.rest.authn.core.wrappers

Class CoreServicesWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.core.CoreServicesWrapper
      • org.forgerock.openam.core.rest.authn.core.wrappers.CoreServicesWrapper

  • public class CoreServicesWrapper
extends CoreServicesWrapper
    A wrapper class around core static class and methods. Providing a wrapper around these methods allows for easy decoupling and unit testing. This class only contains REST authentication specific methods, all more general core methods should be added to CoreServicesWrapper.
